title: Protecting consumers from funny honey (Department of Agriculture - Australian Government)
text: ( Source : Department of Agriculture - Australian Government ) 15 October 2015 The Australian Government has this week moved to strengthen its testing regime for imported honey, to protect consumers from mislabelled and misrepresented products
